{"tid":1532843,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對於直升機飛近集會地點，我有d野想講","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T06:14:03.000Z","uid":57857,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"30c869395942a453837566e959a6e8d6e81d885b","tid":1532843,"uid":57857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"[代開]<br />\n<br />\n首先，我唔係直升機機師<br />\n但據我有限既航空知識<br />\n我唔認為直升機噴螢光粉可行<br />\n第一，架直升機咁高<br />\n第二，直升機旋翼個downwash咁勁<br />\n第三，香港一號風球，又有風又有雨<br />\n以上種種，我覺得要用架直升機係一個指定區域精準咁噴粉係好高難道，甚至近乎無可能<br />\n<br />\n但係，直升機係最好既掩護！<br />\n<br />\n一出直升機，所有人就望曬過去<br />\n我地識得圍魏救趙<br />\n敵方都識得引開你注意<br />\n會唔會係直升機飛近既同時<br />\n有drones靜悄悄咁飛係人群上面灑粉/錄影監視？<br />\n甚至會唔會呢個時候有鬼係人群入面做野？<br />\n再講，今日添馬公園係集會<br />\n如果我係敵方，明知大家會坐係一個指定區域幾個鐘，我一早係公園灑曬螢光粉已經得<br />\n<br />\n不過帶番頭盔先，我唔係現場<br />\n我只係鍵盤戰士<br />\n如果真係有人見到直升機有做野既<br />\n請即刻糾正番我<br />\n<br />\n我開呢個post都係想提醒各位手足，以後見到直升機，就更應該打醒十二分精神，留意隔離左右有無奇怪野發生<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"1145c96c8b9935e4cdb1cc8b80e54a1071ac53e5","tid":1532843,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:29:52.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"3e166da773dd3973d911f16335512114bae61743","tid":1532843,"uid":57857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"輕推"},{"pid":"f38457cd9678770934cebc969f7bf9612578b9be","tid":1532843,"uid":194482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad1e4a72e2569a3d4e0c92d50cca2b7ba6274a94","tid":1532843,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355e871dc1df8a62ebb5c851fbcd50ed2f6fddff","tid":1532843,"uid":148439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:17:35.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"271e51a8b7d3da4d14f362f0293fc4469adc26d2","tid":1532843,"uid":257628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"d672ae432aa3b2e051b319c3fb25125aa8ba24bf","tid":1532843,"uid":194482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:22:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"390f8d7b8b494f3d702145a8f07fe8f1544f2c86","tid":1532843,"uid":80334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:22:16.000Z","msg":"903添馬三罷"},{"pid":"c3f0e96678039f450384c45925c117948754390c","tid":1532843,"uid":80528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"九月三日 三罷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWRbToz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWRbToz.png&h=293f266a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n光復香港 清算警察 人人有責"},{"pid":"9ad88a2c008b5c2e868083d7ae5737a7a6933656","tid":1532843,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:35:20.000Z","msg":"831都有大量直升機 成條街咁多人 灑落去實中到"},{"pid":"404b951f8a2161688493fb4c0b4d59235c362902","tid":1532843,"uid":190895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:36:45.000Z","msg":"其實灑黎做咩？拉人果時照？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7159b20b9b380da8c21002d828c33ff282f6b8d","tid":1532843,"uid":293605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"404b951f8a2161688493fb4c0b4d59235c362902","tid":1532843,"uid":190895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:36:45.000Z","msg":"其實灑黎做咩？拉人果時照？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:48:52.000Z","msg":"可能方便喺